// Flash = a cast-permission window widening [CR#702.8a]: "you may play this
// card any time you could cast an instant" — a May(Cast) row whose window
// is instant speed (deontics §3 Only-refinement, inverted to a grant).
// Functions from any zone the card could be played from.
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Flash",
    template: "flash",
    abilities: [Static(effects: [
        May(Cast(what: Ref(This), window: InstantSpeed)),
    ])],
)
